sub_title: RMG, Capability Manager, Global Commerce at The HEINEKEN Company
summary:
Capability Manager in Revenue & Margin Growth management at Heineken Global Commerce - global pricing platform product owner.

Previously leading Revenue Management Analytics as data science product owner at Heineken Global Commerce.

Before joining Heineken Global Commerce, an OpCo Revenue Manager, Manager at PwC Advisory, Financial Planning & Analysis specialist at Goodyear Dunlop CEE hub. Early career as Analyst in Investment Banking  at UniCredit (M&A, Ljubljana / Vienna). 

Double Degree Master in International Financial Management & Business Economics (IFM) at University of Uppsala (SWE) and University of Groningen (NL). Bachelor at Munich Business School. 

Certified company appraiser in progress. IMB at IEDC Bled in progress.
